public enum PeerGroupConfigFlag
extends Enum<PeerGroupConfigFlag>

Flags used in the configuration of the standard peer group.

Enum Constant Summary
SHUNT_PARENT_CLASSLOADER
          Configures the peer group class loader such that the parent class loader is the non-JXTA ClassLoader instance with which the GenericPeerGroup was constructed, effectively bypassing any Module definitions present in the parent groups' JxtaLoaders.

SHUNT_PARENT_CLASSLOADER

public static final PeerGroupConfigFlag SHUNT_PARENT_CLASSLOADER
Configures the peer group class loader such that the parent class loader is the non-JXTA ClassLoader instance with which the GenericPeerGroup was constructed, effectively bypassing any Module definitions present in the parent groups' JxtaLoaders.
